>Shawn

He peaced out at right as the Attitude Era got kicked off in earnest. And he failed miserably as top babyface of WWF, even getting mercilessly booed by the MSG crowd against heel Sid.

Shawn also had a tendency to screw around in the ring or phone it in if he wasn't interested on the night as well.
